OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be occasional bright
OL,6,For sunny spells on Sunday, although
OL,7,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain are
OL,8,Falso likely, which could turn heavy
OL,9,Fwith some hail and thunder. The brisk
OL,10,Fand gusty southwesterly wind will
OL,11,Fslowly ease.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA few coastal showers
OL,14,Fovernight, but becoming generally dry
OL,15,Finland with clear spells. Turning
OL,16,Fchilly with frost developing in rural
OL,17,Fareas. The odd fog patch forming in
OL,18,Fthe lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
